---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="SocialProof vs Competitors — Testimonial Software Comparisons" description="How does SocialProof compare to Trustpilot, Senja, BirdEye, Podium, NiceJob, Okendo, Feefo, Grade.us, Vocal Video, and 20+ other tools? Honest comparisons for small business owners." canonical="https://socialproof.dev/vs/">
<style>
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    :root {
      --purple: #6c5ce7;
      --purple-light: #a29bfe;
      --dark: #0f0e17;
      --text: #e0dff5;
      --muted: #9b9ab8;
      --card-bg: #211f33;
      --border: #2e2c47;
      --green: #00b894;
    }
    body { font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif; background: var(--dark); color: var(--text); line-height: 1.6; }
    a { color: var(--purple-light); text-decoration: none; }
    a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }

    nav { background: var(--dark); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); padding: 1rem 2rem; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; }
    .nav-logo { font-size: 1.2rem; font-weight: 800; color: var(--text); letter-spacing: -0.5px; }
    .nav-logo span { color: var(--purple-light); }
    .nav-cta { background: var(--purple); color: #fff; padding: 0.5rem 1.25rem; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: 600; font-size: 0.9rem; }
    .nav-cta:hover { background: var(--purple-light); text-decoration: none; }

    .hero { max-width: 760px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 4rem 2rem 2rem; text-align: center; }
    h1 { font-size: 2.2rem; font-weight: 800; line-height: 1.25; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
    h1 em { font-style: normal; color: var(--purple-light); }
    .hero p { font-size: 1.1rem; color: var(--muted); max-width: 560px; margin: 0 auto 2rem; }

    .section-label { max-width: 900px; margin: 2rem auto 0.5rem; padding: 0 2rem; font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: var(--muted); }
    .grid { max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0.5rem 2rem 2rem; display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(260px, 1fr)); gap: 1.25rem; }
    .card { background: var(--card-bg); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 14px; padding: 1.5rem; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.75rem; transition: border-color 0.15s; }
    .card:hover { border-color: var(--purple); text-decoration: none; }
    .card-name { font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--text); }
    .card-tagline { font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--muted); }
    .card-price { font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--muted); border-top: 1px solid var(--border); padding-top: 0.75rem; }
    .card-price strong { color: var(--purple-light); }
    .card-link { font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--purple-light); font-weight: 600; margin-top: auto; }

    .bottom { max-width: 760px; margin: 2rem auto; padding: 0 2rem 4rem; text-align: center; }
    .bottom h2 { font-size: 1.6rem; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
    .bottom p { color: var(--muted); margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
    .cta-btn { display: inline-block; background: var(--purple); color: #fff; padding: 0.85rem 2rem; border-radius: 10px; font-weight: 700; font-size: 1rem; }
    .cta-btn:hover { background: var(--purple-light); text-decoration: none; }
    .sub { font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--muted); margin-top: 0.75rem; }

    footer { text-align: center; padding: 2rem; border-top: 1px solid var(--border); color: var(--muted); font-size: 0.85rem; }
    footer a { color: var(--muted); }
</style>

<nav>
  <a class="nav-logo" href="https://socialproof.dev/"><span>Social</span>Proof</a>
  <a class="nav-cta" href="https://socialproof.dev/#pricing">Try Free</a>
</nav>

<div class="hero">
  <h1>SocialProof vs <em>every competitor</em></h1>
  <p>Honest comparisons to every major testimonial and social proof tool — features, pricing, and who each one is actually built for.</p>
</div>

<!-- ENTERPRISE / AGENCY TOOLS -->
<div class="section-label">Enterprise &amp; Agency Platforms</div>
<div class="grid">
  <a class="card" href="/vs/trustpilot">
    <div class="card-name">SocialProof vs Trustpilot</div>
    <div class="card-tagline">Trustpilot is built for big brands with big budgets. SocialProof gives you first-party testimonials you own and control.</div>
    <div class="card-price">Trustpilot: <strong>$225+/mo</strong> → SocialProof: <strong>free forever</strong></div>
    <div class="card-link">See comparison →</div>
  </a>
  <a class="card" href="/vs/birdeye">
    <div class="card-name">SocialProof vs BirdEye</div>
    <div class="card-tagline">BirdEye is enterprise reputation management at $299–399/mo. SocialProof is the lean, affordable alternative for small teams.</div>
    <div class="card-price">BirdEye: <strong>$299–399/mo</strong> → SocialProof: <strong>$9/mo</strong></div>
    <div class="card-link">See comparison →</div>
  </a>
  <a class="card" href="/vs/podium">
    <div class="card-name">SocialProof vs Podium</div>
    <div class="card-tagline">Podium bundles reviews, messaging, and payments starting at $399/mo. SocialProof keeps it simple: collect, approve, embed.</div>
    <div class="card-price">Podium: <strong>$399–599/mo</strong> → SocialProof: <strong>$9/mo</strong></div>
    <div class="card-link">See comparison →</div>
  </a>
  <a class="card" href="/vs/reputation">
    <div class="card-name">SocialProof vs Reputation.com</div>
    <div class="card-tagline">Reputation.com is built for enterprises managing hundreds of locations. SocialProof is built for the business owner who does it themselves.</div>
    <div class="card-price">Reputation.com: <strong>custom/enterprise</strong> → SocialProof: <strong>$9/mo</strong></div>
    <div class="card-link">See comparison →</div>
  </a>
  <a class="card" href="/vs/widewail">
    <div class="card-name">SocialProof vs Widewail</div>
    <div class="card-tagline">Widewail is enterprise review management at $300+/mo. SocialProof is for founders and small teams who need results, not a dashboard empire.</div>
    <div class="card-price">Widewail: <strong>$300+/mo</strong> → SocialProof: <strong>$9/mo</strong></div>
    <div class="card-link">See comparison →</div>
  </a>
</div>

