    <div class="card-price">Testimonial.io: <strong>$25/mo</strong> → SocialProof: <strong>free forever</strong></div>
    <div class="card-link">See comparison →</div>
  </a>
  <a class="card" href="/vs/boast">
    <div class="card-name">SocialProof vs Boast</div>
